1
00:04:31,062 --> 00:04:32,656
[IN SINDARIN] (Minlû pedich nin...)

2
00:04:35,047 --> 00:04:37,303
(i aur hen telitha.)

3
00:04:38,273 --> 00:04:41,066
(Ú i vethed... nâ i onnad.)

4
00:04:41,091 --> 00:04:43,251
(Boe bedich go Frodo.)

5
00:04:43,926 --> 00:04:46,105
(Han bâd lîn.)

6
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:59,175
(Dolen i vâd o nin.)

7
00:04:59,834 --> 00:05:03,529
(Si peliannen i vâd na dail lîn.)

8
00:05:03,553 --> 00:05:06,909
(Si boe ú-dhannathach.)

9
00:05:13,414 --> 00:05:15,711
(Ae ú-esteliach nad...)

10
00:05:16,086 --> 00:05:18,163
(estelio han...)

11
00:05:19,335 --> 00:05:21,419
(estelio ammen.)

12
00:06:51,394 --> 00:06:54,465
[IN SINDARIN] (Nach gwannatha sin?)

13
00:06:54,490 --> 00:06:57,803
(Ma nathach hi gwannathach or minuial - archened?)

14
00:07:00,399 --> 00:07:02,942
[IN SINDARIN] (Ú-ethelithon.)

15
00:07:03,745 --> 00:07:05,733
(Estelio guru lîn ne dagor.)

16
00:07:05,757 --> 00:07:07,318
(Ethelithach.)

17
00:07:07,342 --> 00:07:09,565
(Ú-bedin o gurth ne dagor.)

18
00:07:09,589 --> 00:07:12,075
(O man pedich?)

19
00:07:17,037 --> 00:07:19,037
(Edra le men...)

20
00:07:19,163 --> 00:07:20,420
(...men na guil edwen...)

21
00:07:22,215 --> 00:07:26,839
(haer o auth...a nîr...a naeth.)

22
00:21:56,198 --> 00:21:58,152
[IN SINDARIN] (Tollen i lû.)

23
00:22:00,159 --> 00:22:04,081
(I chair gwannar na Valannor. Si bado... no círar.)

24
00:24:39,269 --> 00:24:42,458
[IN SINDARIN] (A im ú-'erin veleth lîn?)

25
00:24:44,029 --> 00:24:45,794
(Gerich meleth nîn, ada.)

26
00:25:37,036 --> 00:25:40,205
GALADRIEL [IN SINDARIN]: <i> The world is changed.
(I amar prestar aen.)</i>

27
00:25:40,767 --> 00:25:42,767
I feel it in the water,
(Han mathon ne nen,)

28
00:25:43,169 --> 00:25:45,169
I feel it in the earth,
(han mathon ne chae,)

29
00:25:46,941 --> 00:25:49,164
and I smell it in...
(a han noston ned...)

30
00:25:50,012 --> 00:25:51,265
...the air.
(...'wilith.)

31
00:44:47,643 --> 00:44:51,407
[IN SINDARIN] Well done, Brego, my friend.
(Mae carnen, Brego, mellon nîn.)

32
00:45:27,850 --> 00:45:28,910
[IN SINDARIN] (Le abdollen.)

33
00:46:01,008 --> 00:46:03,844
[IN SINDARIN] Thank you.
(Hannon le.)

34
00:53:23,631 --> 00:53:25,453
[IN SINDARIN] (Boe a hyn...)

35
00:53:25,803 --> 00:53:27,555
(Neled herain...                            )

36
00:53:27,580 --> 00:53:28,946
(Neled herain... dan caer menig!)

37
00:53:30,675 --> 00:53:32,893
[IN SINDARIN] (Si beriathar hyn ammaeg na ned Edoras...)

38
00:53:32,918 --> 00:53:34,169
Aragorn.

39
00:53:34,303 --> 00:53:36,970
(Nedin dagor hen ú-'erir ortheri.)

40
00:53:37,887 --> 00:53:39,250
(Natha daged dhaer!)

41
00:58:15,283 --> 00:58:17,852
[IN SINDARIN] (Ú-moe edhored, Legolas.)

42
00:59:40,990 --> 00:59:43,243
Well met, Haldir!
(Mae govannen, Haldir!)

43
01:01:57,214 --> 01:01:58,770
[IN SINDARIN] O, Children of Eru... (A Eruchîn...)

44
01:01:58,976 --> 01:02:01,073
...show them no mercy... (...ú-dano i faelas a hyn...)

45
01:02:01,945 --> 01:02:04,365
(an uben tanatha le faelas!)

46
01:03:23,987 --> 01:03:24,658
(Dartho!)

47
01:03:55,484 --> 01:03:56,694
(Tangado a chadad!)

48
01:04:05,674 --> 01:04:08,022
[IN SINDARIN] (Faeg i-varv...dîn na lanc...)

49
01:04:08,047 --> 01:04:09,699
(...a nu ranc.)

50
01:04:09,727 --> 01:04:11,445
(Leithio i philinn!)

51
